Letters to the Editor:
   A Leaner IBM,
   But Not Meaner
As a computer-industry watcher, I am well aware of the
problems IBM is currently facing in the market. It is
attempting to solve its problems, not, in my opinion, trying
to set direction for the nation.
   Patricia A. Lauletta
   Vice President
   Information Services
   Datapro
   Delran, N.J.